The damage to equipment is a paladin/ranger/warrior's most expensive cost. <br>
After years of experience, the warrior learns how to help preserve his<br>
armor and weapons through proper care, By observing armorsmiths repair<br>
and fix the different pieces, they learn how to help maintain their<br>
equipment.  This is an autoskill.<br>
